Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.core

Class Summary
Definition Definition is a class representing a narrative description of a Sense.
GlobalInformation GlobalInformation is a class representing administrative information and other general attributes of a LexicalResource.
LexicalEntry LexicalEntry is a class representing a lexeme in a given language.
LexicalEntryTest Tests methods of LexicalEntry class
LexicalResource LexicalResource is a class representing the entire resource.
LexicalResourceTest Tests methods of LexicalResource class
Lexicon Lexicon is a class containing all the lexical entries of a given language within the entire resource.
LexiconTest Tests methods of Lexicon class
Sense Sense is a class representing one meaning of a lexical entry.
The Sense class allows for hierarchical senses in that a sense may be more specific than another sense of the same lexical entry.
SenseTest Tests methods of Sense class
Statement Statement is a class representing a narrative description and refines or complements Definition.
TextRepresentation TextRepresentation is a class representing one textual content of diverse Uby-LMF classes, such as Definition, SenseExample or Statement.
